fire storm
Level-7th
CastingTime-1Action
Range/Area-150ft
School-Evocation
Attack/Save-DEX
Damage-7d10
OtherInfo-                A storm made u of sheets of roaring flame aears in a location you choose within range. The area of the storm consists of u to ten 10-foot cubes, which you can arrange as you wish. Each cube must have at least one face adjacent to the face of another cube. Each creature in the area must make a Dexterity saving throw. It takes 7d10 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.
